src:
【獨家】【金主與愛的距離】女版小玉尬炫富網紅　美麗妄娜肉貼金主烏鴉
05 Nov 2019, 08:58 by 娛樂組, 攝影組
有40.6萬人訂閱的YouTuber美麗妄娜，曾因買了50包吸管拍影片，遭批不環保、浪費，並被封為「女版小玉」，雖然行事有爭議，但外型亮麗的她依舊受到許多男性粉絲追捧，感情狀態神祕，最近卻被本刊直擊，早就尬上經紀公司老闆，也是知名YouTuber的烏鴉。











美麗妄娜目前是「惡棍娛樂」旗下的網紅，而惡棍娛樂就是由炫富網紅烏鴉所投資的經紀公司，2人經常在YouTube上合作，私下竟也有不少情欲流動的互動，發展出了一段職場戀情。本刊直擊，美麗妄娜陪烏鴉過生日、看電影，當街摸肚、摳奶，使出渾身解數狂撩烏鴉，最後還把老闆打包帶上陽明山。








　
影城慶生　摸肚又摸頭
10月29日深夜將近12點，美麗妄娜和烏鴉悄悄出現在台北信義威秀影城，這天正是烏鴉生日，2人看起來心情相當愉悅，光是排隊買票就自拍了好幾張。在等待看電影的時候，美麗妄娜還幫蹲在鐵門前的烏鴉拍影片，經過本刊確認，這支影片就是烏鴉在謝謝粉絲的生日祝福，烏鴉在影片裡還搞神祕地說「我不能透露我在哪裡」，殊不知早就被本刊全都錄。


烏鴉善於撒錢拍開箱文，YouTube已有73.3萬人追蹤。（翻攝自烏鴉YouTube）

到了凌晨2點多，2人看完電影後，烏鴉趕緊衝到外面抽菸解癮，而美麗妄娜則一路緊貼著烏鴉，還忍不住伸手摸摸烏鴉的肚子，摸完肚子之後又摳烏鴉的奶頭，接著又摸頭，大頭小頭都摸了不打緊，還幫烏鴉整理衣領，看起來對於烏鴉的肉體相當有興趣，藏不住噴發愛欲的美麗妄娜，趕緊跟烏鴉上了計程車。


烏鴉是有名的炫富網紅，還曾拿出存摺證明自己有2,300萬元存款。（翻攝自烏鴉YouTube）

　
上山泡湯　偷親猛撩男
計程車先是在永吉路附近暫停，2人到便利商店採買食物，為晚點可能很耗力的約會行程補充乾糧，在排隊結帳的時候，美麗妄娜又忍不住主動偷親了烏鴉，撩男功力相當精彩，十足的肉體行動派。


美麗妄娜（右）在限動上頻繁發文幫烏鴉慶生，其實當晚也親陪烏鴉過生日。（翻攝自美麗妄娜IG）

做好一切準備後，搭載著猴急小倆口的計程車，就直接往陽明山仰德大道開去，似乎要找個地方泡湯，不過說時遲那時快，小倆口還沒泡到湯，就先發現了狗仔的鏡頭，還使出大絕到警察局報案，讓這段生日現泡之旅，暫時劃下句點。


烏鴉（左）創立了網紅經紀公司，旗下藝人就是美麗妄娜。（翻攝自美麗妄娜IG）

擁有73萬人訂閱的烏鴉，曾在直播平台上捐獻10萬元，只求跟直播主吃頓飯，還不時大手筆抽禮物送粉絲，因此被網友稱為炫富，但他事後表示，自己並非含著金湯匙出生，經濟來源都來自投資的副業，光是成立網紅經紀公司，不到1年就花了2千多萬元。
更新時間｜2019.11.05 07:30

[Exclusive] [the distance between the gold master and the love] female version of the small jade show off the rich net red beautiful Dina meat stick the gold master crow
05 Nov 2019, 08:58 by Entertainment Group, Photography Group
YouTuber beautifully subscribed to 406,000 people. She bought a 50-pack straw to make a film. It was not environmentally friendly, wasted, and was named as a "female version of Xiaoyu". Although she is controversial, she still looks good. It has been sought after by many male fans, and its emotional state is mysterious. Recently, it has been directly attacked by this magazine. It has long been a boss of a brokerage company and a crow of well-known YouTuber.











Beautiful Dina is currently the net of "The villain entertainment", and the villain entertainment is the brokerage company invested by Hyunfu.com. The two people often cooperate on YouTube. In private, there are also many passionate interactions. A period of workplace love. The journal hits, the beautiful Dina with the crows birthday, watching movies, when the street touches the belly, sucks the milk, makes all the arrogant crows, and finally packs the boss with Yangmingshan.









Studio City Qingsheng
Nearly 12 o'clock in the middle of the night on October 29, beautiful Dina and crows appeared quietly in Taipei Xinyi Weixiu Studios. This is the birthday of the crows. The two people seem to be quite happy. They just took a few tickets and bought them. While waiting to watch the movie, the beautiful Dina also helped the crow in front of the iron gate to make a film. After confirming this film, this film is the birthday greeting of the crow in thank you fans. The crow still has a mysterious saying in the film, "I can't I have revealed where I am," I don't know if I have been recorded in this magazine.


The crow is good at throwing money out of the box, and YouTube has tracked 733,000 people. (Reflected from Raven YouTube)

At 2 o'clock in the morning, after watching the movie, the crows rushed to the outside to smoke and addiction, while the beautiful Dina was clinging to the crow all the way, and could not help but reach out and touch the crow's stomach. The crow's teat, then touched the head, the big head and the small head touched it, and helped the crow to sort the collar. It seemed to be quite interested in the crow's flesh. He couldn't hide the beautiful grace of erupting love, and quickly followed the crow. taxi.


The crow is a famous Hyun Fu net red, and has also used the passbook to prove that he has a deposit of 23 million yuan. (Reflected from Raven YouTube)


Going up the mountain to soak the soup
The taxi was first suspended near Yongji Road. Two people went to the convenience store to buy food. They added dry food for a date that might be very laborious. When they lined up for checkout, the beautiful Dina couldn’t help but steal the crow. The skill is quite wonderful, full of physical action.


Beautiful Dina (right) frequently issued a text to help the crow to celebrate the birth, in fact, the night also accompanied the crow to birthday. (Reviewed from the beautiful Dina IG)

After all the preparations, the taxis carrying the monkeys and the couples will go straight to Yangdeshan Yangde Avenue. It seems that they have to find a place to bathe, but when it is too late, the couple have not yet soaked in the soup. First, I found out the paparazzi's lens, and also made a big report to the police station, so that this birthday is a bubble trip, temporarily draw a period.


The Raven (left) founded the Net Red Brokerage Company, and its artists are beautiful and graceful. (Reviewed from the beautiful Dina IG)

The crow, who has a subscription of 730,000 people, once donated 100,000 yuan on the live broadcast platform. He only wanted to eat dinner with the live broadcaster. He also sent gifts to the fans from time to time. Therefore, he was called a show-off by netizens, but he said afterwards that he himself It was not born with a gold spoon. The source of the economy came from the sideline of investment. It was just the establishment of the network red brokerage company, which cost more than 20 million yuan in less than a year.
